l metadata; (2) ≥1.5 BLEU gain over m4 Adapter in zero-shot settings; (3) t-SNE plots confirm clean clustering of styles across languages and structures across domains; (4) ablation shows meta-curriculum improves generalization by 20% in low-data regimes.",
